347
00:34:11,864 --> 00:34:13,264
What?

348
00:34:13,824 --> 00:34:15,025
Why are you surprised?

349
00:34:15,105 --> 00:34:17,665
Nut is so irresistibly charming.

350
00:34:18,225 --> 00:34:21,145
No man or woman can resist his charm.

351
00:34:21,225 --> 00:34:23,185
Plus, you've lost your memory.

352
00:34:23,264 --> 00:34:26,944
I don't know if you were into men
or women before this.

353
00:34:27,025 --> 00:34:28,585
I don't trust you.

354
00:34:29,304 --> 00:34:32,145
So, do you want Nut to be your boyfriend?

355
00:34:33,465 --> 00:34:35,264
Boyfriend?

356
00:34:37,904 --> 00:34:39,304
What do you mean?

357
00:34:39,384 --> 00:34:41,105
I only want to be a bear.

358
00:34:42,344 --> 00:34:43,824
A bear?

359
00:34:45,225 --> 00:34:47,545
I guess your memory is still hazy.

360
00:34:47,625 --> 00:34:48,784
Let's put it like this.

361
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:50,824
Seeing someone romantically…

362
00:34:50,904 --> 00:34:53,784
it's that feeling you get
when you really like someone.

363
00:34:54,344 --> 00:34:56,424
When you're near them

364
00:34:56,505 --> 00:34:58,225
and lock eyes with them,

365
00:34:58,305 --> 00:35:00,305
your heart starts beating fast.

366
00:35:08,105 --> 00:35:11,305
