369
00:35:16,625 --> 00:35:18,585
It's another kind of heartbeat.

370
00:35:18,665 --> 00:35:22,265
It's like your heart will beat
through your chest.

371
00:35:22,345 --> 00:35:25,785
You feel like you're floating on air,

372
00:35:27,065 --> 00:35:28,985
and you're the only people in the world.

373
00:35:32,384 --> 00:35:34,904
When I locked eyes with Nut earlier,

374
00:35:38,145 --> 00:35:40,585
-my heart was beating really fast.
-What?

375
00:35:43,585 --> 00:35:45,785
But I think it was from chasing Kuenchai.

376
00:35:46,345 --> 00:35:47,985
I saw a documentary.

377
00:35:48,065 --> 00:35:51,225
When you're tired,
your heart beats a little faster.

378
00:35:51,785 --> 00:35:54,185
