379
00:35:55,904 --> 00:35:56,785
Really?

380
00:35:57,345 --> 00:35:58,185
Really.

381
00:36:04,985 --> 00:36:07,864
If he's not your type,

382
00:36:08,985 --> 00:36:10,904
