383
00:36:12,185 --> 00:36:13,384
What favor?

384
00:36:13,864 --> 00:36:17,105
Can you get Nut to like me?

385
00:36:18,145 --> 00:36:20,145
Make him want to be my boyfriend.

386
00:36:23,625 --> 00:36:24,625
Of course.

387
00:36:24,705 --> 00:36:25,745
Really?

388
00:36:26,225 --> 00:36:28,025
You're the sweetest.

389
00:36:28,105 --> 00:36:30,785
Thank you so much.

390
00:36:32,424 --> 00:36:34,065
So tell me,

391
00:36:35,105 --> 00:36:36,225
