392
00:36:38,465 --> 00:36:40,545
Do I have to explain it all over again?

393
00:36:41,105 --> 00:36:42,105
Yes.

394
00:36:45,225 --> 00:36:48,904
Whatever you know about Nut, spit it out.

395
00:36:48,985 --> 00:36:50,384
I'm ready to hear it.

396
00:36:51,625 --> 00:36:52,985
