420
00:38:04,985 --> 00:38:07,545
Come on. You're overthinking it.

421
00:38:08,065 --> 00:38:11,625
Who wouldn't want
a cute little guy like you around?

422
00:38:12,585 --> 00:38:14,904
Am I right? Don't be so dramatic.

423
00:38:14,985 --> 00:38:16,225
Let's continue.

424
00:38:17,105 --> 00:38:18,185
Okay.

425
00:38:18,265 --> 00:38:21,384
Do you know any of his secrets?

426
00:38:21,464 --> 00:38:24,225
Something nobody else knows.

427
00:38:24,904 --> 00:38:28,785
Things he does in the bedroom
or what he keeps under his bed.

428
00:38:30,505 --> 00:38:32,225
There's nothing under his bed.

429
00:38:34,625 --> 00:38:37,305
I mean…

430
00:38:37,985 --> 00:38:39,864
I mean that kind of stuff.

431
00:38:39,944 --> 00:38:41,625
You know?

432
00:38:43,985 --> 00:38:47,065
