438
00:39:37,705 --> 00:39:40,625
But when I do it, he gives me an earful.

439
00:39:47,225 --> 00:39:48,345
Pribpree.

440
00:39:50,065 --> 00:39:51,105
Pribpree.

441
00:39:55,825 --> 00:39:58,065
