456
00:40:42,944 --> 00:40:45,305
But it feels like three years.

457
00:40:45,864 --> 00:40:46,985
Is that so?

458
00:40:47,745 --> 00:40:50,185
So what is Nut like at work?

459
00:40:51,305 --> 00:40:54,105
He's very focused on his work.

460
00:40:54,705 --> 00:40:56,305
When he's working,

461
00:40:56,785 --> 00:40:59,864
