462
00:41:00,785 --> 00:41:03,025
He looks ten times cooler than usual.

463
00:41:04,464 --> 00:41:06,345
But when there's urgent work,

464
00:41:06,904 --> 00:41:09,825
he likes to go off and work by himself.

465
00:41:10,825 --> 00:41:12,705
When he has writer's block,

466
00:41:13,785 --> 00:41:15,825
