489
00:42:50,384 --> 00:42:53,625
Is he actually your son,
and I'm just adopted?

490
00:42:53,705 --> 00:42:55,505
Have you worked it out just now?

491
00:42:55,585 --> 00:42:56,705
What?

492
00:42:57,904 --> 00:43:00,105
Gosh. Mr. Sitha.

493
00:43:00,185 --> 00:43:03,145
Don't come crying
when I'm not around anymore.

494
00:43:03,225 --> 00:43:05,225
-Gosh.
-How fierce.

495
00:43:05,305 --> 00:43:07,185
I think I would be glad.

496
00:43:07,265 --> 00:43:08,785
-Dad.
-Hey.

497
00:43:08,864 --> 00:43:11,864
You should start looking
for your real parents.

498
00:43:12,944 --> 00:43:15,345
Have you found your parents yet?

499
00:43:15,424 --> 00:43:18,065
Stop it, Dad. You too, Mom.

500
00:43:18,145 --> 00:43:19,225
-You're adopted.
