513
00:44:16,105 --> 00:44:17,105
Juea.

514
00:44:18,384 --> 00:44:20,424
You can pick anyone you want.

515
00:44:20,505 --> 00:44:23,305
You can pick this one, this one,

516
00:44:23,384 --> 00:44:24,705
or this one.

517
00:44:24,785 --> 00:44:27,384
But you can't pick this guy.

518
00:44:28,705 --> 00:44:31,065
