he plays instruments,

521
00:44:36,185 --> 00:44:37,464
and he can ride a motorbike.

522
00:44:37,545 --> 00:44:39,705
-He's perfect.
-That's true.

523
00:44:40,745 --> 00:44:42,265
What's the problem?

524
00:44:42,745 --> 00:44:44,705
-Shut up.
-What's wrong with him?

525
00:44:46,265 --> 00:44:48,265
Listen. He's just a kid.

526
00:44:48,345 --> 00:44:50,025
And he has no experience.

527
00:44:50,105 --> 00:44:51,745
Can we really trust him?

528
00:44:51,825 --> 00:44:55,464
Haven't you heard people say
that you should never work with kids?

529
00:44:55,545 --> 00:44:56,785
If you don't trust me…

530
00:45:00,145 --> 00:45:02,225
you could try going out with me.

531
00:45:06,025 --> 00:45:07,225
Hey!

532
00:45:09,225 --> 00:45:10,225
What is he doing here?

533
00:45:10,305 --> 00:45:11,665
-Surprise!
-Juea.

534
00:45:13,864 --> 00:45:16,705
I'm just kidding. You're way too serious.

535
00:45:18,105 --> 00:45:20,705
-Hello, everyone.
-Hi.

536
00:45:20,785 --> 00:45:22,464
Hello.

537
00:45:22,545 --> 00:45:25,864
-Hello, Juea.
-Long time no see.

538
00:45:25,944 --> 00:45:27,745
This is my guy.

539
00:45:27,825 --> 00:45:31,904
Prepare the set. Get the costumes.
